userinterface.graph

Class SeriesSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • userinterface.graph.SeriesSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, SettingOwner

    public class SeriesSettings
extends java.util.Observable
implements SettingOwner
    A class representing a series of a Graph. This class should not be used to modify data, use Graph for this. The intention is that this class represents all properties (colour, lines, heading, etc.) other than data.
